Organization
-------------------
http://ideacellular.com
Idea Cellular, Aditya Birla Group
It is one of the major telecom companies in India.


Problem
-------------
Sql injection in Corporate Account Login

Dates
--------------
Reported: 17th March 2009
Fixed:       23rd March 2009

Credits
----------
Aseem Jakhar - Member NULL security community http://null.co.in

Problem Description
-----------------------------
There was a sql injection vulnerability in the corporate Account login
on the ideacellular.com website. They were doing client side validation
only, which could be easily bypassed. It could lead to unauthorized
access and database manipulation.


